title: Adam Lambert, Demi Lovato put feud rumours to rest
text: Adam Lambert, Demi Lovato put feud rumours to rest Sunday, 25 October 2015 (14 minutes ago) Things are fine between singer Demi Lovato and Adam Lambert, as the two exchanged pleasantries on social media.
